<p>I have datagrid with hidden buttons, how to make button in row visible after row selection using Style.Triggers?</p>  <pre><code>    &lt;Grid&gt;     &lt;DataGrid ItemsSource="{Binding Items}"&gt;         &lt;DataGrid.RowStyle&gt;             &lt;Style TargetType="DataGridRow"&gt;                 &lt;Style.Triggers&gt;                     &lt;Trigger Property="IsSelected" Value="True"&gt;                      &lt;/Trigger&gt;                 &lt;/Style.Triggers&gt;             &lt;/Style&gt;         &lt;/DataGrid.RowStyle&gt;         &lt;DataGrid.Columns&gt;             &lt;DataGridTemplateColumn Header="" Width="15" MinWidth="15" &gt;                 &lt;DataGridTemplateColumn.CellTemplate&gt;                     &lt;DataTemplate&gt;                         &lt;Border Margin="0" Background="Gray"&gt;                             &lt;Button x:Name="CurrentButton" Content="{Binding number}" Visibility="Hidden"&gt;&lt;/Button&gt;                         &lt;/Border&gt;                     &lt;/DataTemplate&gt;                 &lt;/DataGridTemplateColumn.CellTemplate&gt;             &lt;/DataGridTemplateColumn&gt;         &lt;/DataGrid.Columns&gt;     &lt;/DataGrid&gt; &lt;/Grid&gt; </code></pre>